{
  "texts": [
    "However, appropriate legal frameworks -such as liability laws, must be established before deploying AI agents in screening, assessment, or treatment (Sejnowski, 2024).",
    "When implemented responsibly, AI can support data-driven decisions and optimize resources, enhancing the effectiveness of communication-focused public health initiatives.",
    "The domains of professional practice include advocacy, supervision of graduate clinicians in training, the education of SLPs, research in the discipline and administration.",
    "Again, each domain is considered individually from the viewpoint of how AI may automate and augment it.",
    "SLPs serve as essential advocates for individuals with communication disorders, promoting awareness and equitable access to care."
  ]
}